    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this first-person speedrunning challenge, every movement counts. Nail your jumps, optimize your path, and keep that momentum flowing!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708070/extras/a13edc3b18d2e60b4328ca4111bf358a.poster.avif?t=1767489070\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1708070/extras/a13edc3b18d2e60b4328ca4111bf358a.webm?t=1767489070\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gainers</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect jumps don’t just keep you moving — they <i>boost</i> your speed. Chain them together, and you'll turn into a momentum-fueled blur. Stopping? That’s for quitters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vertical Gainer</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perfect jumps also add verticality, opening up unexpected shortcuts and sneaky routes to maximize your gains.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Vibrant Environments</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >From molten volcanoes to frozen peaks, relive the chaotic charm of <i>Speedrun Académie</i> with its iconic fire-and-ice level.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Leaderboard</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb the leaderboard and prove you’re the fastest. Only the best will claim their spot among the speedrunning champions.</p>",
